				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10621807/scp-4727#post-4183801</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2019 01:26:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>minmin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>560062</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">explain</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I'll update after the contest to make it clearer but essentially Rogers the cop steals the gun, either intentionally or unintentionally, from Inez's murder scene<br /> Either before or after that, he discovers that it's magic. He gets what he wants from the gun then passes it on to his hooker/one-time-lover Thomas as a sugar daddy gift. Thomas instead uses it to discover that he's cheating on her and kills him instead before dying in a shootout herself.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>I'll write test logs eventually but I think it's getting too loaded as it is.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
